sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant PROXY as HTTPProxy
    participant MINER as MinerNode
    participant TX as TransactionService
    participant CHAIN as ChainService
    participant CONS as Consensus
    participant PEERS as Peers

    Note over MINER,CONS: Miner starts mining immediately on startup
    MINER ->> CONS: begin mining loop
    CONS -->> MINER: new proof of work found
    MINER ->> CHAIN: apply empty block when no transactions
    CHAIN -->> MINER: block accepted as head
    MINER ->> PEERS: broadcast block
    PEERS -->> MINER: peer acknowledgements

    FE ->> PROXY: send signed transaction
    PROXY ->> MINER: forward signed transaction
    MINER ->> TX: validate transaction
    TX -->> MINER: transaction accepted
    MINER ->> CHAIN: queue transaction for next block
    MINER ->> CONS: continue mining with transaction
    CONS -->> MINER: block with transaction found
    MINER ->> CHAIN: apply new block
    CHAIN -->> MINER: block accepted to the longest chain
    MINER ->> PEERS: broadcast block with transaction
    PEERS -->> MINER: peer acknowledgements
    FE ->> PROXY: request transaction status
    PROXY ->> MINER: check inclusion
    MINER -->> PROXY: confirmed in chain
    PROXY -->> FE: show confirmed to user
